item.title: resources
item.description: Below you will find many external sites that relate to anything cyber. I’ll do my best at expanding and organizing this list moving forward. Of the sites listed below, thank you site/project owners and communities for sharing such great information! OSINT OSINTCURIO.US - https://osintcurio.us/ OSINT Framework - https://osintframework.com/ awesome osint - https://github.com/jivoi/awesome-osint Search Engines Google dorking(hacking) - https://google.com https://www.exploit-db.com/google-hacking-database https://www.google-dorking.com/ https://www.dorksearch.com/ https://www.blackhat.com/presentations/bh-europe-05/BH_EU_05-Long.pdf Google Earth - https://earth.google.com/web/ WolframAlpha - https://www.wolframalpha.com/ Bing - https://bing.
